name: Dream Catcher
description:
Featured at the 2012 Artcrank show, this limited edition piece is a must-have for any bike enthusiast, dream catcher collector, poster hoarder, or anyone trying to take their living space to the next level. 

Poster is on sale for $25 until Christmas.

Details:
16" x 20" 1 Color Screen Print, standard frame size.
Limited edition print size of 50 numbered and signed by the artist. 
Printed on 95 lb. Reincarnation cover matte.
Shipping can take up to 8 days from the time shipped.
